      "widgets_values": [
        "1. It is necessary to install the [ComfyUI_bitsandbytes_NF4 plugin](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI_bitsandbytes_NF4) in advance.\n\n2. The model file needs to be downloaded: https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/flux1-dev-bnb-nf4/blob/main/flux1-dev-bnb-nf4-v2.safetensors.\n\n3. Please install the model file to the `comfyui/models/checkpoints` directory.\n\n4. Due to the good understanding ability of the Flux model for prompts, negative prompts in the workflow do not need any content input.\n\n1. 需要预先安装 [ComfyUI_bitsandbytes_NF4 插件](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI_bitsandbytes_NF4)。\n\n2. 需要下载模型文件：https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/flux1-dev-bnb-nf4/blob/main/flux1-dev-bnb-nf4-v2.safetensors。\n\n3. 模型文件请安装至 `comfyui/models/checkpoints` 目录。\n\n4. 由于 Flux 模型对提示词良好的理解能力，在工作流中的负向提示词并不需要任何的内容输入。\n\nsource: https://comfyui-wiki.com/tutorial/advanced/flux1-comfyui-guide-workflow-and-examples"
